author: thorsten
msg: Fixing bug related to the chainmeta module. It was not possible to use variables that not have been defined in the forrest-core.xconf with forrest:XXX. This change looks up the name if the original lookup returns null. This way you can use forrest:xxx for any property you define via the plain properties or xml.
